It&#x27;s a crappy hack, but paste this into your JavaScript console:<p><pre><code>    function exportFile(path) { var b = new Blob([FS.readFile(path).buffer], {&#x27;type&#x27;: &#x27;text/plain&#x27;}); var u = URL.createObjectURL(b); window.location.href = u; }
</code></pre>
And then you can run this to export files:<p><pre><code>    exportFile(&quot;/usr/local/share/vim/vimrc&quot;);</code></pre>
